      • rfc2543toRfc3261RouteUpdate

        public void rfc2543toRfc3261RouteUpdate()
        Changes form RFC2543 Strict Route to RFC3261 Lose Route.

        The Request-URI is replaced with the last value from the Route header, and that value is removed from the Route header.
